dct_description_sm: 3 sheets joined. Wood block print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the upper right. Relief shown pictorially. Includes lists of block names, schools, shrines, temples, and banks. Includes the national flags, distance chart and legend. 1 map: col., mounted on paper; 34 x 60 cm., folded in cover 28 x 20 cm., in envelope 30 x 22 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
